{"tid":1630852,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"成條街冇晒鐵欄啦！","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:59:26.000Z","uid":161260,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d86f5bb146ef9af2e8d3eab1c13fa3a992261071","tid":1630852,"uid":161260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"鐵欄用一個少一個..<br />\n拆完後消失晒<br />\n要set rb 越黎越少道具<br />\n<br />\n點算好"},{"pid":"48caf9a4fa1a811912c25891470ae09b12babf41","tid":1630852,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:54:37.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"d176276328dc0d6f58172745167e3d10e5315c0b","tid":1630852,"uid":59868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:55:28.000Z","msg":"磨機"},{"pid":"11d733549979db34a91c377e0fd9f2b6583c9fda","tid":1630852,"uid":193233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"咁就咪鬼守啦"},{"pid":"35585650b5befa04f550aa9a09bcd4b3074f1ae5","tid":1630852,"uid":68598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:59:26.000Z","msg":"次次一有RB就守上癮<br />\n唔SET搵垃圾阻一阻咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}